item.title: HacktivityCon CTF: Bullseye
item.description: It’s clear to see from the content of my blog that my expertise lies in web-based exploits. However, I have mentioned before wanting to branch out and diversify my skillset in hacking; and while I definitely have more knowledge in web exploits, I also know a thing or two about pwning. Hacktivity Con CTF was a competition that ran this month, introducing several different challenges that I sunk my teeth into.
